di Tarchich</i> e <i>di Antoura,</i>

191
00:14:33,418 --> 00:14:35,418
<i>di Damour,</i>

192
00:14:36,043 --> 00:14:37,710
<i>di Achié...</i>

193
00:14:40,335 --> 00:14:41,626
Buongiorno, Sig. Toni.

194
00:14:42,960 --> 00:14:44,751
Può venire un momento?

195
00:14:46,376 --> 00:14:47,501
A fare che?

196
00:14:47,710 --> 00:14:49,793
C'è stato un malinteso,

197
00:14:50,293 --> 00:14:52,751
