204
00:15:19,501 --> 00:15:21,793
<i>Perché continuiamo a lottare?</i>

205
00:15:22,043 --> 00:15:24,835
<i>Perché esiste la resistenza libanese?</i>

206
00:15:25,043 --> 00:15:27,710
